room_title: Escape room "Hyde" by Labyrinth Escape Games in Portland
review: Just completed Jekyll/Hyde with the minutes to spare! Staff is friendly and helpful... but not too helpful! We will definitely be back.

room_title: Escape room "Hyde" by Labyrinth Escape Games in Portland
review: Super fun!  We solved the Hyde room with just a few minutes to spare. Whew!  The room was creative and challenging. It says beginner level difficulty.  But we thought it was hard!  Next time we're in Portland, we'll def check out more rooms here.

room_title: Escape room "Hyde" by Labyrinth Escape Games in Portland
review: We just finished the Hyde room. It was very well done with great puzzles. They have the best set design of any of the rooms we've been to. Highly recommend!
